name: BARBIE GIRL - acrylic necklace, hot pink, silver glitter, laser cut, princess, stripper

This super awesome pendant is made of high quality laser cut acrylic in bright hot pink on top of silver glitter. Bold, fun, and lightweight! The acrylic layers in my products are literally welded, NOT glued, for superb quality!

• necklace length approx 18" w/ lobster claw clasp
